Meeting Description:

This conference will focus on the concept of 'complement', which was brough=
t into french grammar by Beauz=E9e and Du Marsais to refer to some specific=
 kind of syntagmatic relation.

Depuis son introduction dans la terminologie linguistique par Du Marsais et=
 Beauz=E9e, la notion de compl=E9ment n'a cess=E9 de muer et de se d=E9mult=
